      "summary_raw": "Father\u2019s Day is just around the corner and it\u2019s not just another date on the calendar. For retailers, it\u2019s a chance to connect with their communities and help customers celebrate the fathers and father figures in their lives in a meaningful way. The good news? No matter what you sell, there\u2019s room to tap into [&hellip;]",
